1 - No purchase necessary. Open to new JCP Members and existing Individual Full JCP Members converting to Associate Membership, 18 or older. Government employees, Oracle employees and their family members, and residents of Quebec, Italy, and countries under US embargo are not eligible to participate. Ends: December 31, 2017 at 11:59 PM. For complete Official Rules, see <a href="http://oracle.com/webfolder/s/delivery_production/docs/FY16h1/doc38/Disclaimer-LPD100635965.pdf">http://oracle.com/webfolder/s/delivery_production/docs/FY16h1/doc38/Disclaimer-LPD100635965.pdf</a>.<P>

